# UCAB - Features

## Overview

The UCAB Cab Booking System provides a complete ride-booking experience for users and drivers. The application is designed using the MERN Stack and includes authentication, cab booking, ride management, and booking history features.

---

## Core Features

### 1. User and Driver Authentication

The system provides secure authentication for both users and drivers.

#### User Authentication
- User Registration
- User Login
- Password Encryption
- JWT Authentication
- Profile Management

#### Driver Authentication
- Driver Registration
- Driver Login
- Driver Verification
- Secure Session Management

---

### 2. Cab Type Selection

Users can choose different cab categories based on their travel needs.

Available Cab Types:

- Mini
- Sedan
- SUV
- Premium Cab

Benefits:
- Flexible ride options
- Fare comparison
- Better travel experience

---

### 3. Ride History and Receipt Download

The application maintains a complete history of rides.

Features:

- View Previous Rides
- Ride Details
- Driver Information
- Fare Information
- Download Receipt
- Payment History

Benefits:

- Easy expense tracking
- Travel record maintenance
- Receipt accessibility

---

### 4. Scheduled Bookings

Users can schedule rides in advance.

Features:

- Select future date
- Select pickup time
- Confirm booking
- Receive booking confirmation

Benefits:

- Convenient planning
- Timely transportation
- Better ride availability

---

### 5. Booking Cancellation and Rescheduling

Users can modify existing bookings.

Cancellation Features:

- Cancel upcoming rides
- Receive cancellation confirmation

Rescheduling Features:

- Change pickup time
- Change destination
- Reassign available driver

Benefits:

- Flexible booking management
- Improved user convenience

---

