---

## Technologies Used

- React.js
- Node.js
- Express.js
- MongoDB
- JWT Authentication
- Axios
- Bootstrap

---

## Outcome

The UCAB Features Module provides secure authentication, flexible booking options, ride tracking, booking management, and improved user convenience for both riders and drivers.

